Description: The 'matchmaker' package provides flexible dictionary-based
    cleaning that allows users to specify implicit and explicit missing data,
    regular expressions for both data and columns, and global matches, while
    respecting ordering of factors. 
URL: https://repidemicsconsortium/matchmaker, https://github.com/reconhub/matchmaker
